â”‚   â”‚   Purpose: Displays a persistent notification bar at the top of the screen if DNS records are not fully verified.
â”‚   â”‚   Details:
â”‚   â”‚     - Consumes `DnsStatusContext` to get `overallDnsStatus`, `dnsContextLoaded`, and `isDnsModalOpenGlobally`.
