â”‚   â”‚     - Visibility is further refined by `shouldShowBasedOnPageEligibility`: only shows on `/dns-confirmation`, pages after it in `FORM_FLOW_ORDER`, or pages not in `FORM_FLOW_ORDER` at all.
â”‚   â”‚     - Clicking the bar calls `showDnsModal()` from the context to open the `DnsConfigurationModal`.
â”‚   â”‚   Usage: Rendered globally by `src/core/App.tsx`.
