â”‚   â”‚     - **Auto-opens modal**: If `selectedDnsProvider` is set in context on page load (e.g., from notification bar click), the modal opens automatically for that provider.
â”‚   â”‚     - **No longer displays overall DNS status directly** (handled by global notification bar).
â”‚   â”‚     - **No longer renders its own modal instance.**
â”‚   â”‚     - Retains local `handleVerifyDns` function, but this is for the page's own verification logic if any is reinstated; the global modal uses its own verification logic defined in `App.tsx`.
â”‚   â”‚     - "Previous" button navigates to `/info-clarification`.
â”‚   â”‚     - "Next Step" button navigates to `/website-tracking`. Button is enabled even if DNS is not fully verified, showing a toast warning instead.
