â”‚   â””â”€â”€ ğŸ“„ differ.ts
â”‚       Purpose: Backend-specific adapter for the V2 template diffing service.
â”‚       Details:
â”‚         - Extends `DifferV2Core` from `src/shared/services/differ.ts`.
â”‚         - Currently provides no backend-specific overrides, simply inherits core diffing logic.
â”‚         - Exports `DifferV2` class.
â”‚       Usage: Used internally by backend functions like `generate-email-changes` and `manage-pending-changes` when V2 diff calculations are needed.
